---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Inflection Point Partners">
	<!-- Page Intro -->
	<div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:max-w-none">
			<div class="mt-24 sm:mt-32 lg:mt-40">
				<div class="max-w-2xl">
					<h1>
						<span class="block font-display text-base font-semibold text-neutral-950">About us</span>
						<span class="sr-only"> - </span>
						<span class="mt-6 block max-w-5xl font-display text-5xl font-medium tracking-tight text-neutral-950 sm:text-6xl">
							Pushing the boundaries of human potential
						</span>
					</h1>
					<div class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-xl text-neutral-600">
						<p>
							We believe that our strength lies in identifying the inflection points where small changes create exponential results in fitness, health, and longevity.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<!-- Team Section -->
	<div class="mt-24 sm:mt-32 lg:mt-40">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:max-w-none">
				<!-- Border -->
				<div class="border-t border-neutral-950/10"></div>

				<!-- Arthur Etchells -->
				<div id="arthur" class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 pt-12 sm:pt-16 lg:grid-cols-4 xl:gap-8">
					<div>
						<h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-neutral-950">
							Arthur Etchells
						</h2>
					</div>
					<div class="lg:col-span-3">
						<div class="space-y-6 text-base text-neutral-600">
							<p>
								Arthur is an inveterate builder of companies, products and experiences. Most recently, he built Constructor.com from 0 to 10s of millions in revenue.
							</p>
							<p>
								<a href="https://arthuretchells.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-neutral-950 font-semibold hover:text-neutral-700 transition-colors">
									arthuretchells.com →
								</a>
							</p>
						</div>

						<div class="mt-12">
							<h3 class="font-display text-base font-semibold text-neutral-950">Philosophy</h3>
							<div class="mt-6 space-y-8">
								<div>
									<h4 class="font-display text-base font-semibold text-neutral-950">Transformative Wellness</h4>
									<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-600">
										At the edge of human potential lies uncharted territory. Arthur's mission is to guide
										individuals through evidence-based approaches to fitness, health, and longevity that
										challenge conventional thinking and deliver measurable results.
									</p>
								</div>

								<div>
									<h4 class="font-display text-base font-semibold text-neutral-950">The Event Horizon Approach</h4>
									<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-600">
										Just as an event horizon marks the point of no return in physics, Arthur believes in
										identifying the critical moments in health and fitness where transformation becomes
										inevitable. These inflection points, when properly leveraged, create lasting change
										that stretches beyond ordinary expectations.
									</p>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Border -->
				<div class="border-t border-neutral-950/10 mt-24"></div>

				<!-- Alex Chisler -->
				<div id="alex" class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 pt-12 sm:pt-16 lg:grid-cols-4 xl:gap-8">
					<div>
						<h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-neutral-950">
							Alex Chisler
						</h2>
					</div>
					<div class="lg:col-span-3">
						<div class="space-y-6 text-base text-neutral-600">
							<p>
								Alex combines technical brilliance and years of experience from Facebook with a passion for human performance optimization.
							</p>
							<p>
								<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/alexander-chisler/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-neutral-950 font-semibold hover:text-neutral-700 transition-colors">
									LinkedIn →
								</a>
							</p>
						</div>

						<div class="mt-12">
							<h3 class="font-display text-base font-semibold text-neutral-950">Professional Experience</h3>
							<div class="mt-6 space-y-8">
								<div>
									<h4 class="font-display text-base font-semibold text-neutral-950">Software Engineer at Facebook</h4>
									<p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Jul 2020 - Sep 2024 · 4 yrs 3 mos</p>
									<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-600">
										Integrity team member, working on critical systems to ensure platform safety and security.
									</p>
								</div>

								<div>
									<h4 class="font-display text-base font-semibold text-neutral-950">Engineering Team Lead at YunoJuno</h4>
									<p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Jan 2019 - Jul 2020 · 1 yr 7 mos</p>
									<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-600">
										Led a team of 4 people, reported to CTO. Built the search infrastructure, extended billing tools, and supported compliance work for UK freelancer regulations.
									</p>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>
